report.subtitle: Passed in the reigns of King Charles I and King Charles II

section.head: CHRONOLOGICAL TABLE OF THE TITLES OF ALL THE ACTS OF PARLIAMENT PASSED IN THE REIGNS OF KING CHARLES I. AND KING CHARLES II.
